    "actual_capabilities": [
      "Explains the required markdown and YAML structure for Claude Code plugin agents.",
      "Shows how to write triggering descriptions with concrete example blocks.",
      "Guides model, color, and tool selection for agent frontmatter.",
      "Provides system prompt structure for responsibilities, process, standards, and output format.",
      "Includes a shell validator for checking agent file structure and common quality issues.",
      "Provides complete examples for common agent types and triggering patterns."
    ],
    "limitations": [
      "It guides agent creation but does not deploy agents automatically.",
